      "content": "that's a good start, really captures the atmosphere. i want to zoom in a bit more on some of the actual characters or people the protagonist might see while walking through these streets. i want to show the \"danger\" through the types of people hanging out on the corners or lurking in the shadows. can you describe a few different groups of people that would make the protagonist feel like they're in a high-crime area and shouldn't stay too long?",
